description.name: 260pcs wire stripper terminals pliers set
description.long_desc:
The multifunctional stripper allows you to strip insulation from single-core cables and individual strands of multi-core cables. The device also allows for crimping connector terminals.


The set includes a set of cable connectors 100pcs and a set of cable ties.


Product Features:


front mechanism
hardened cable cutter
the two-material handle ensures high comfort at work
jaws made of high-quality hardened steel
possibility of crimping connector terminals 22-10 AWG


Technical Specifications:


Working range: 0.2 - 6 mm


Supported connector terminals: 1.5 - 6 mm


Overall length: 205mm
